snippet.title: Live Coding: Learning TypeScript
snippet.description:
TypeScript looks like it might be the future of JavaScript. It adds type checking and some other features that JavaScript is lacking. It compiles down to regular JavaScript so it can be integrated to existing work. Let's explore the language and learn how to write it, compile it, and package libraries.
